body:
For the next Champion Release, can we get a Zyra update instead, to make her viable mid again? It seems like the perfect time to do it, now that champions like Xin, Urgot, WW and Evelynn all got their reworks. 

I don&#039;t know about the rest of you, but I used to adore playing Zyra Mid. I miss it so much &amp; I wouldn&#039;t mind if we got a Zyra Mid Update next instead of a New Champ Release. 

{{champion:143}}
